Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.97,0:00:06.11,Default,,0,0,0,,The Tree of Harmony remains one\Nof the most powerful sources
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.21,0:00:08.28,Default,,0,0,0,,of magic known to ponydom.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.38,0:00:11.78,Default,,0,0,0,,And though it has been at the\N"root" of Magic and Friendship
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.88,0:00:15.48,Default,,0,0,0,,from the moment it was planted,\Nits ways are mysterious.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.58,0:00:18.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Almost as if it has\Na mind of its own.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.62,0:00:21.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Mind? Pfft. It's a tree.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.76,0:00:23.89,Default,,0,0,0,,A tree that grew\Na castle!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.49,0:00:28.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Was that before or after\NDiscord made chocolate rain?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.23,0:00:30.00,Default,,0,0,0,,[whisper] After.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.40,0:00:32.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm never going to\Nlearn Pony history!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.62,0:00:36.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You can all show me what you've\Nlearned on tomorrow's test!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.60,0:00:39.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Friendship's effect on the\Ncourse of Equestrian History.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.44,0:00:44.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Remember, study groups are\Nboth fun AND effective!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.28,0:00:48.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Sandbar: So.. who wants to\Nstudy together?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.58,0:00:51.52,Default,,0,0,0,,With other students?\NThis is Equestria!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.72,0:00:55.05,Default,,0,0,0,,If you want the real scoop,\Nthere's only one place to go!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.49,0:01:00.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello, oh magical\NEquestrian tree!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.10,0:01:04.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you tell me {\i1}everything{\i0} I\Nneed to know about friendship?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.18,0:01:58.48,Default,,0,0,0,,The Elements of Harmony\Ngrew the tree?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.79,0:02:02.23,Default,,0,0,0,,[sigh] No. The pillars\Ngrew the tree.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.32,0:02:05.65,Default,,0,0,0,,The tree grew the elements. And\Nthen the box with six locks.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.76,0:02:07.63,Default,,0,0,0,,But our professors\Nfound six keys
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.73,0:02:09.40,Default,,0,0,0,,and unlocked\Nthe box.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.00,0:02:11.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so gonna fail..
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.67,0:02:13.80,Default,,0,0,0,,You guys! Check\Nthis out!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.54,0:02:17.87,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a plumbing diagram\Non how to fix a sink.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.64,0:02:21.84,Default,,0,0,0,,What does that have to do\Nwith Equestrian History?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.94,0:02:25.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing. I just can't believe\Nthat's how sinks work!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.35,0:02:26.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Where's Yona?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.65,0:02:36.55,Default,,0,0,0,,[chuckle] Apparently, yaks no\Nlove study groups!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.66,0:02:38.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Shhhh. Haha.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.76,0:02:46.16,Default,,0,0,0,,SPIDER! NO!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.74,0:02:54.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey Cozy. What are\Nyou doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.51,0:02:57.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I volunteered to help Professor\NSparkle organize these books.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.98,0:03:00.68,Default,,0,0,0,,So? Experts on\NFriendship History yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.78,0:03:03.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I think I'd be better off\Nstudying the plumbing book.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.25,0:03:04.92,Default,,0,0,0,,This stuff is impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.09,0:03:11.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, come on, Gallus! With good\Nfriends and solid study habits,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.59,0:03:13.69,Default,,0,0,0,,anything is possible!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.13,0:03:16.23,Default,,0,0,0,,How about you just tell us
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.33,0:03:18.16,Default,,0,0,0,,what's on tomorrow's\Ntest, Professor?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.27,0:03:20.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah! Please! Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.20,0:03:23.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Now hold on a sec. I can't\Ngive y'all a sneak peek!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.64,0:03:25.81,Default,,0,0,0,,That there wouldn't be honest!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.58,0:03:35.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Ahem. Golly, it's so inspiring how\Nrelaxed you all are about
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.15,0:03:39.02,Default,,0,0,0,,studying friendship\Nconsidering your disadvantage.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.82,0:03:41.29,Default,,0,0,0,,What cute pony mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.59,0:03:44.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Just consider where\Nyou all came from!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.16,0:03:47.49,Default,,0,0,0,,If Sandbar hadn't sacrificed\Nso much of his time
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.59,0:03:50.96,Default,,0,0,0,,to get you up to speed? Who\Nknows how behind you'd be?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.57,0:03:53.94,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not--
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.03,0:03:57.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, growing up as a\Nlove-starved changeling!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.54,0:04:00.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Or hiding underwater from an\Nevil king all those years!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.81,0:04:04.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Trusting any creature\Nmust be so hard for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.65,0:04:07.58,Default,,0,0,0,,And Griffons never want\Nto be around any creature.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.68,0:04:09.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Even other griffons!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.42,0:04:11.95,Default,,0,0,0,,And dragons are so\Nfierce compared to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.15,0:04:14.78,Default,,0,0,0,,There must be days you\Ncan't wait to get away
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.89,0:04:16.89,Default,,0,0,0,,from all us cute ponies.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.29,0:04:20.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Everypony know "yaks\Nthink yaks are best".
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.56,0:04:22.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Making friends with\Nany other creature
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.13,0:04:23.97,Default,,0,0,0,,must seem like a step down.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.27,0:04:27.60,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just so impressive\Nhow you keep trying
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.70,0:04:29.20,Default,,0,0,0,,to understand friendship,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.30,0:04:31.73,Default,,0,0,0,,even though it isn't\Nin your nature.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.11,0:04:36.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! I'll let you borrow my\Nnotes! It's what friends do!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.78,0:04:37.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be right back!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.11,0:04:42.38,Default,,0,0,0,,We should get\Nback to studying...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.19,0:04:55.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Could you stop that clicking!?\NI'm trying to focus.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.93,0:04:56.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Dude...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.96,0:04:59.76,Default,,0,0,0,,What? We have a test. I\Ndon't know every detail
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.87,0:05:02.84,Default,,0,0,0,,about every adventure the\Nprofessors went on like you do.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.14,0:05:05.11,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why we're\Nstudying together.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.21,0:05:08.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Right. To help us\N"disadvantaged" creatures.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.68,0:05:10.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Yona confused. Why\Nwe all upset?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.65,0:05:22.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I only glanced at\Nthat plumbing book,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.49,0:05:25.22,Default,,0,0,0,,but I'm pretty sure this\Nisn't supposed to be here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.13,0:05:28.50,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.90,0:05:32.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Dragon. Strange Magical Cave.\NWhat do you think I'm doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.55,0:05:49.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Did we know this was down here?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.95,0:05:52.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think anypony\Nknows this is down here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.36,0:05:58.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.69,0:06:01.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Headmare Twilight?\NWhere are we?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.39,0:06:03.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Where you need to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.40,0:06:05.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh. Yona confused.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.17,0:06:09.64,Default,,0,0,0,,It is as I feared. You are not\None. What has happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.74,0:06:12.87,Default,,0,0,0,,We were studying Friendship's\Neffect on History but then...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.07,0:06:16.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Since friendship just isn't in\Nour nature, what's the point?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.24,0:06:20.11,Default,,0,0,0,,You do not believe\Nfriendship is in your nature?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.51,0:06:22.81,Default,,0,0,0,,That is NOT ACCEPTABLE!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.42,0:06:27.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Our headmare is\Nglowing, you guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.22,0:06:29.35,Default,,0,0,0,,What is going on!?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.66,0:06:32.06,Default,,0,0,0,,We should probably get back\Nto studying for the test.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.49,0:06:34.89,Default,,0,0,0,,A test. Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.60,0:06:38.07,Default,,0,0,0,,By sunrise, this\Ndoor will be closed.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.17,0:06:40.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Finish the test before\Nthen and you may go.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.03,0:06:43.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Fail the test and\Nhere you will stay.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.91,0:06:51.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.48,0:06:54.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.55,0:06:57.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.46,0:07:06.19,Default,,0,0,0,,OH!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.36,0:07:10.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Mt. Aris!?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.93,0:07:12.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Headmare Twilight\Nsent me home?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.27,0:07:16.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait. Am I suspended?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.90,0:07:17.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.14,0:07:19.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Anygriff here?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.87,0:07:20.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.81,0:07:21.94,Default,,0,0,0,,They must be topside.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.84,0:07:24.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.18,0:07:25.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.48,0:07:29.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Agh!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.45,0:07:33.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.92,0:07:38.52,Default,,0,0,0,,THE STORM KING?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.63,0:07:39.96,Default,,0,0,0,,He's BACK?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.30,0:07:44.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Big room. No exits.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.53,0:07:45.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Big deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.04,0:07:53.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Not cool..
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.74,0:07:59.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing for yaks\Nto be afraid of.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.68,0:08:03.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Just empty cave. Nothing\Nin here can hurt...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.44,0:08:06.34,Default,,0,0,0,,...Yona!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.39,0:08:13.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Ugh. Things like this just don't\Nhappen in the Dragonlands.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.86,0:08:17.93,Default,,0,0,0,,-Huh?\N-And I told her she was the\Ncutest pony of all ponies!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.43,0:08:21.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Oooh! Aren't you just\Nthe most ADORABLE thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.80,0:08:22.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Come join us!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.97,0:08:26.81,Default,,0,0,0,,No. On so many levels, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.24,0:08:32.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.75,0:08:35.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Come sit by me and let's\Ncompliment each other!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.28,0:08:37.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Agh!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.39,0:08:42.56,Default,,0,0,0,,[gasp] Why do you look\Nlike that?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.76,0:08:43.73,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.82,0:08:44.85,Default,,0,0,0,,We all look the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.16,0:08:45.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Not me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.46,0:08:50.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course not you,\NYour Majesty.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.10,0:08:52.10,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll go drain the love from\Nthose pathetic ponies
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.20,0:08:54.57,Default,,0,0,0,,in Ponyville just\Nas you ordered!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.17,0:08:59.34,Default,,0,0,0,,[gasp] NO!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.94,0:09:05.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, thank HEAVENS\Nwe've found you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.71,0:09:08.91,Default,,0,0,0,,There's an emergency\Nand we need YOU, Sandbar!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.25,0:09:12.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! My first friendship adventure!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.89,0:09:14.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes! Count me in!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.45,0:09:15.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been waiting\Nfor this--
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.12,0:09:17.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait. The others!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.56,0:09:19.03,Default,,0,0,0,,We don't need {\i1}them{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.23,0:09:21.20,Default,,0,0,0,,We need you! Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.07,0:09:33.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, Gallus.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.41,0:09:34.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Get it together.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.88,0:09:35.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Deep breaths.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.18,0:09:40.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah...ah...ah choo!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.59,0:09:50.33,Default,,0,0,0,,OK, if this is a test,\Nthere's got to be a way out.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.42,0:09:53.76,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just a puzzle...\Nthat will squash you
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.36,0:09:56.29,Default,,0,0,0,,if you don't\Nfigure it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.64,0:10:06.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah ha!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.64,0:10:08.54,Default,,0,0,0,,No pressure.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.58,0:10:16.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Oops!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.28,0:10:34.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Grrrr.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.30,0:10:39.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Look. I have to get out of here\Nand find my friends,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.11,0:10:41.81,Default,,0,0,0,,so just tell me what I have\Nto do to pass this test.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.91,0:10:43.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not afraid of anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.94,0:10:45.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Um. I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.41,0:10:48.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Seems like she's afraid to be\Ncute and adorable, doesn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.62,0:10:51.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Or maybe she's just\Nafraid to admit
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.48,0:10:55.35,Default,,0,0,0,,she {\i1}likes{\i0} being\Ncute and adorable.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.56,0:10:56.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm hm.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.22,0:10:58.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Just this once.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.63,0:11:02.23,Default,,0,0,0,,[ahem] May I have\Nsome tea, please?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.33,0:11:06.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, but you can't have tea\Nif you aren't dressed for it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.57,0:11:09.54,Default,,0,0,0,,OK. But let's keep\Nthis between us.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.72,0:11:25.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah!\N[crash]
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.07,0:11:41.80,Default,,0,0,0,,YONA NEED HELP!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.90,0:11:44.97,Default,,0,0,0,,WHERE YONA'S FRIENDS\NWHEN YONA NEEDS THEM?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.32,0:11:52.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh!?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.15,0:11:56.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Yona no mean to scream...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.08,0:11:59.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Yona love making friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.52,0:12:01.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Spiders... friends?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.89,0:12:07.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait. What little spider say?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.67,0:12:14.94,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened\Nto you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.51,0:12:16.83,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.72,0:12:21.74,Default,,0,0,0,,You never saw ANY\Nof that, got it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.35,0:12:28.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe the others got out\Nalready and we're the last ones?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.22,0:12:31.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. That totally seems like\Nsomething they would do...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.62,0:12:34.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmph. Any other dragon or griffon\Nwould save themselves
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.76,0:12:36.69,Default,,0,0,0,,and get out of this crazy cave.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.99,0:12:39.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Guess we aren't just {\i1}any{\i0}\Ndragon and griffon anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.03,0:12:42.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Guess not. You go that way.\NI'll check over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.94,0:12:55.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait. I really should\Nfind my friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.14,0:12:59.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Darling, it was so generous\Nof you to take the time
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.75,0:13:02.38,Default,,0,0,0,,to teach those other\Ncreatures about friendship.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.48,0:13:05.98,Default,,0,0,0,,But.. if you're going to join us\Nand do something that really
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.09,0:13:10.26,Default,,0,0,0,,makes a difference, we need to\Nknow where your loyalty lies.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.76,0:13:14.80,Default,,0,0,0,,You do want to impress\Nus, don't you, Sandbar?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.74,0:13:23.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.97,0:13:25.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Ocellus?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.44,0:13:26.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Go away.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.74,0:13:29.47,Default,,0,0,0,,We're still in those weird\Ncaves beneath the school!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.58,0:13:31.05,Default,,0,0,0,,We've got to get out of here!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.25,0:13:36.59,Default,,0,0,0,,[gasp] Chrysalis!\NWhere's Ocellus!?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.78,0:13:40.05,Default,,0,0,0,,[sob] It's me! I'm HIDEOUS!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.86,0:13:45.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello!?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.73,0:13:47.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are--Whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.03,0:13:51.90,Default,,0,0,0,,SHHHHH! The Storm\NKing will hear you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.00,0:13:53.20,Default,,0,0,0,,The Storm King?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.30,0:13:54.47,Default,,0,0,0,,He was defeated.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.57,0:13:55.67,Default,,0,0,0,,We're still under\Nthe school.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.77,0:13:57.40,Default,,0,0,0,,This is all just\Nsome crazy test!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.21,0:14:02.88,Default,,0,0,0,,OK, that's horrifying.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.48,0:14:06.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't find any\Nhippogriffs or seaponies!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.51,0:14:08.14,Default,,0,0,0,,They must all be captured!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.38,0:14:12.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Gallus! Get back down here!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.20,0:14:24.63,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not real!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.03,0:14:26.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.13,0:14:28.30,Default,,0,0,0,,He's back and I'm never going\Nto see another sunset
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.40,0:14:31.20,Default,,0,0,0,,or fly through a cloud\Nbank or study plumbing!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.30,0:14:33.63,Default,,0,0,0,,He's going to take\Naway everything I love...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.74,0:14:36.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to be trapped\Ndown here forever!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.34,0:14:38.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm afraid of\Nbeing trapped too.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.71,0:14:41.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm scared of\Nsmall spaces.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.78,0:14:42.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.88,0:14:43.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.12,0:14:46.15,Default,,0,0,0,,And I was stuck in a\Nroom that kept shrinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.25,0:14:49.55,Default,,0,0,0,,But I realized I had to face my\Nfear and I found the way out.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.76,0:14:52.16,Default,,0,0,0,,This is your test. He\Nisn't really here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.46,0:14:55.93,Default,,0,0,0,,But what if he is..!?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.13,0:14:58.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Then tell him exactly\Nwhat you think of him!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.97,0:15:04.24,Default,,0,0,0,,H-h-hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.44,0:15:05.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Storm King!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.84,0:15:08.44,Default,,0,0,0,,You're nothing but\Na big ole bully
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.74,0:15:11.94,Default,,0,0,0,,with a silly name\Nand a goofy crown!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.15,0:15:16.49,Default,,0,0,0,,You thought you could scare us\Ninto doing whatever you wanted!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.68,0:15:21.02,Default,,0,0,0,,But we learned that together\Nwe're STRONGER than you!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.22,0:15:22.89,Default,,0,0,0,,And now that\Nwe're rid of you,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.99,0:15:27.63,Default,,0,0,0,,we're gonna SOAR THROUGH THE\NSKY and go on adventures
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.73,0:15:32.40,Default,,0,0,0,,and NEVER GIVE YOU\NANOTHER THOUGHT. EVER!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.74,0:15:37.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Haha!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.10,0:15:39.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.24,0:15:41.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I told him!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.61,0:15:44.78,Default,,0,0,0,,OK, hug time later.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.88,0:15:46.45,Default,,0,0,0,,We still have to get\Nback to the library.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.58,0:15:49.78,Default,,0,0,0,,You're a changeling.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.88,0:15:51.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Just.. change back.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.55,0:15:52.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.72,0:15:57.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe my past\Nwas so horrible,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.32,0:15:59.99,Default,,0,0,0,,it's still inside me just\Nwaiting to come out again!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.39,0:16:01.66,Default,,0,0,0,,That's ridiculous.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.76,0:16:03.63,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not who you are anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.73,0:16:04.90,Default,,0,0,0,,You've changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.40,0:16:08.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe we can't really\Nchange THAT much.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.70,0:16:10.43,Default,,0,0,0,,[mumbling] I like cute, silly stuff!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.64,0:16:12.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, what?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.17,0:16:14.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I LIKE cute,\Nsilly stuff!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.11,0:16:18.91,Default,,0,0,0,,But ever since school started,\NI've realized that sometimes
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.11,0:16:21.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I kinda don't mind cute stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.79,0:16:28.26,Default,,0,0,0,,If a dragon like me can\Nadmit she likes... tea parties,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.45,0:16:30.95,Default,,0,0,0,,that's proof we\NCAN change.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.26,0:16:34.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I was gonna invite you to a\Ntop-secret tea party with me,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.16,0:16:36.43,Default,,0,0,0,,but if you want\Nto stay down here...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.93,0:16:39.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, no! I wanna come!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.70,0:16:42.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought that\Nmight work.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.60,0:16:43.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.14,0:16:48.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Where's Yona\Nand Sandbar?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.84,0:16:50.24,Default,,0,0,0,,The way out\Nis closing!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.34,0:16:51.87,Default,,0,0,0,,We aren't leaving\Nwithout them.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.95,0:16:55.15,Default,,0,0,0,,YONA FIND YOU GUYS!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.55,0:16:56.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Argh!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.55,0:16:59.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Yona. Who's\Nyour.. spider army?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.79,0:17:03.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Yona always scared of spiders\Nbut then Yona meet Spindle!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.99,0:17:08.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Yona realize no\Nreason to be afraid!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.73,0:17:10.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Spiders and yak friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.83,0:17:14.13,Default,,0,0,0,,So Yona ask new friends for\Nhelp finding old friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.33,0:17:17.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you think your new friends\Ncan help us find Sandbar?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.04,0:17:23.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Of all the strange things\Nthat have happened tonight,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.64,0:17:25.51,Default,,0,0,0,,that's the strangest, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.75,0:17:31.25,Default,,0,0,0,,OK. Enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.35,0:17:33.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not going anywhere\Nwithout my friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.32,0:17:37.62,Default,,0,0,0,,So you don't care about\Nanypony but your friends?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.82,0:17:40.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you really\Nthat selfish?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.29,0:17:43.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Honestly, you really are\Nsuch a disappointment.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.93,0:17:45.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I've always looked up to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.37,0:17:46.84,Default,,0,0,0,,You would never turn\Nyour back on each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.93,0:17:48.43,Default,,0,0,0,,And that's what\Nmakes you strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.54,0:17:50.37,Default,,0,0,0,,And now I have a group\Nof friends that I think
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.47,0:17:52.24,Default,,0,0,0,,is every bit as\Namazing as yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.54,0:17:54.64,Default,,0,0,0,,If I have to give up on\Nthem to make you proud,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.74,0:17:56.57,Default,,0,0,0,,then you aren't the\Nponies I thought you were.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.68,0:17:58.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't care if\NI disappoint you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.61,0:17:59.88,Default,,0,0,0,,You disappoint me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.22,0:18:07.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you just tell our professors\Nyou were disappointed in them!?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.52,0:18:10.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Something tells me those\Nweren't actually our professors.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.79,0:18:14.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Besides, they tried to get\Nbetween me and my friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.46,0:18:16.76,Default,,0,0,0,,That's all very sweet.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.86,0:18:18.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Now can we please\Nget out of here?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.04,0:18:32.21,Default,,0,0,0,,You! You're not Headmare\NTwilight, are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.81,0:18:36.18,Default,,0,0,0,,[gasp] You're the Tree\Nof Harmony!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.72,0:18:40.42,Default,,0,0,0,,The Tree of Harmony turned\Ninto a sparkly version
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.52,0:18:42.69,Default,,0,0,0,,of our headmare to talk to us?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.09,0:18:44.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Did I miss a chapter in class?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.23,0:18:48.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Like all living things,\NI change as I grow.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.33,0:18:50.83,Default,,0,0,0,,As I have grown, so\Nhave my abilities.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.93,0:18:53.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm a bit rusty\Non Pony history,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.57,0:18:56.04,Default,,0,0,0,,but since when does the Tree\Nof Harmony trap creatures
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.14,0:18:58.01,Default,,0,0,0,,in a cave with their\Nbiggest fears!?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.61,0:19:01.61,Default,,0,0,0,,You chose what you saw\Nin my roots, not me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.31,0:19:06.01,Default,,0,0,0,,[gasp] Our friendship got\Nus past our fears!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.11,0:19:09.34,Default,,0,0,0,,You were more concerned with\Neach other's well being
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.45,0:19:10.22,Default,,0,0,0,,than your own.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.62,0:19:12.69,Default,,0,0,0,,You were strong when\Nyour friends were weak.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.89,0:19:15.22,Default,,0,0,0,,You let each other in and\Nshowed that you would be there
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.32,0:19:16.79,Default,,0,0,0,,for each other,\Nno matter what.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.19,0:19:19.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Friendship IS in\Nyour nature.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.13,0:19:29.26,Default,,0,0,0,,We just learned a friendship\Nlesson from a tree, didn't we.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.17,0:19:33.27,Default,,0,0,0,,You're all right!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.37,0:19:35.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I came back with my\Nnotes and saw this
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.34,0:19:36.97,Default,,0,0,0,,and didn't know\Nwhat to think.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.08,0:19:38.91,Default,,0,0,0,,We're better than\Nall right!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.11,0:19:41.78,Default,,0,0,0,,We just got tested by\Nthe Tree of Harmony!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.88,0:19:44.31,Default,,0,0,0,,And we totally passed!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.92,0:19:47.42,Default,,0,0,0,,The Tree of\NHarmony? Here?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.52,0:19:49.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah! Well. Below here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.79,0:19:50.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Under the school!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.02,0:19:54.05,Default,,0,0,0,,We found this and went down and\Nmet the Tree and Gallus was all
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.26,0:19:56.26,Default,,0,0,0,,"friendship is NOT\Nin our nature"
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.36,0:19:58.03,Default,,0,0,0,,and the tree was like WHAT!?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.13,0:19:59.53,Default,,0,0,0,,And it tested us!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.03,0:20:01.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Long story short.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.60,0:20:03.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Friendship IS in our nature.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.70,0:20:05.33,Default,,0,0,0,,The Tree said so.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.74,0:20:08.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess we should tell somepony\Nthere's a giant magical hole
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.77,0:20:09.77,Default,,0,0,0,,in the library.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.58,0:20:12.25,Default,,0,0,0,,[clang] Or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.35,0:20:14.58,Default,,0,0,0,,We have to tell our\Nprofessors about this!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.68,0:20:15.55,Default,,0,0,0,,They won't believe--
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.65,0:20:16.48,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.88,0:20:17.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Why no?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.98,0:20:20.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Because... it's my fault!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.02,0:20:23.05,Default,,0,0,0,,You were all getting\Nalong so well
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.16,0:20:26.16,Default,,0,0,0,,and I felt left out.\NI was jealous.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.36,0:20:29.93,Default,,0,0,0,,And it upset you so much the\NTree of Harmony had to test you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.23,0:20:33.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! I'm gonna get\Nexpelled for sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.10,0:20:36.77,Default,,0,0,0,,[sobbing] Please don't tell\Nanypony about this!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.87,0:20:38.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Especially the Professors!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.20,0:20:39.00,Default,,0,0,0,,PLEASE! PLEASE! PLEASE!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.11,0:20:39.88,Default,,0,0,0,,OK!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.97,0:20:44.17,Default,,0,0,0,,[yawn] I'm actually too tired\Nto do anything right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.38,0:20:46.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. But we can't\Ngo to sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.75,0:20:47.95,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll miss the test.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.35,0:20:50.22,Default,,0,0,0,,The TEST! I\Nalmost forgot.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.65,0:20:53.35,Default,,0,0,0,,We're all gonna fail.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.59,0:21:02.03,Default,,0,0,0,,What if I tell Professor Sparkle\NI needed help organizing
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.13,0:21:04.56,Default,,0,0,0,,these books and you were all\Nkind enough to pitch in?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.66,0:21:06.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll get you an extension!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.70,0:21:10.27,Default,,0,0,0,,[yawn] Thanks, Cozy.\NThat's nice of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.67,0:21:13.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm just so sorry I\Ncaused all of this.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.94,0:21:15.51,Default,,0,0,0,,You're such good friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.71,0:21:18.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry I ever doubted you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.78,0:21:20.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Mmmm. No prob.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.18,0:21:24.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Friendship is.... Zzzzzzz.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.42,0:21:25.72,Default,,0,0,0,,You get some rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.92,0:21:27.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't give any of\Nthis another thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.05,0:21:30.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Just let Cozy take\Ncare of everything....
